question: Question: This quantity determines the efficiency of conversion of spatial anisotropy to momentum-space anisotropy in quark-gluon matter.  [10] Name this quantity defined as the ratio of shear stress to shear rate for a fluid. It's measured in poise and superfluids don't have any.
